snippet.title: Jumpman Longplay (C64) [50 FPS]
snippet.description:
Follow me on Twitter @ https://twitter.com/Al82_Retro
Read my article about the game @ http://www.vintageisthenewold.com/retro-revisited-jumpman
Developed by Randy Glover and published by Epyx in 1983

TAS recording

Quite a remarkable game - each level is complete different, adding new mechanics and surprises. Fiendishly hard, but very cool!
